{"product_id":"code-9-flagged","title":"CODE-9 FLAGGED","description":"\u003cp\u003e260 GSM. Premium Fabric with Raglan Sleeves. Front \u0026amp; Back Print. 100% French Terry Cotton. Gender-Neutral. Boxy Fit. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis premium 260 GSM T-shirt from Drip Studios is designed for those who like their style bold and unapologetic. Featuring classic raglan sleeves, it delivers enhanced comfort, mobility, and a distinct athletic-inspired silhouette. The front showcases the Drip Studios brand print with a clean, confident presence, while the back makes a powerful statement with the phrase “Are You Flagged and Certified Lover.” Crafted from high-quality French terry cotton, this tee offers durability, breathability, and all-day comfort. CODE 9 is made for individuals who wear their mindset as confidently as their style.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the t-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to maintain fabric quality and print longevity. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to avoid shrinkage. Store in a cool, dry place to preserve the fabric and prints.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM fabric for a structured, premium feel. Raglan sleeves for improved comfort and a relaxed yet refined fit. Boxy, oversized silhouette suitable for both men and women. Unisex design crafted to complement diverse body types. Soft, breathable French terry cotton ensures lasting comfort and durability.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46881407664282,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46881407697050,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46881407729818,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46881407795354,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46881407828122,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00076copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440450","url":"https:\/\/dripdrip.in\/products\/code-9-flagged","provider":"DRIP STUDIOS","version":"1.0","type":"link"}